his case, the Fly's Eye constraints, although\nmore model dependent, turn out to be competitive with other currently available\nconstraints on TeV-scale gravity which are mainly based on interactions\nassociated with Kaluza-Klein gravitons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Nov 2001 17:14:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2001 08:55:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
